Sentencas: The efficiency of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) is heavily dependent on the electrocatalytic activity of the cathode toward the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR).
Titulo: Single crystalline La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 microcubes as cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In order to achieve better cathode performance, single crystalline La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 (LSM) microcubes with the {200} facets have been synthesized by the hydrothermal method.
Titulo: Single crystalline La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 microcubes as cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: It is found that the LSM microcubes exhibit lower polarization resistance than the conventional polycrystalline La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 powder in air from 700 degrees C to 900 degrees C.
Titulo: Single crystalline La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 microcubes as cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The ORR activation energy of the LSM microcubes is lower than that of the conventional powder.
Titulo: Single crystalline La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 microcubes as cathode of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The ORR kinetics for the microcubes is limited by the charge transfer step while that for the conventional powder is dominated by the oxygen adsorption and dissociation on the cathode surface.
Titulo: Single crystalline La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 microcubes as cathode of solid oxide fuel cell
